-- Guindos Says Spain Must Show Finances, Services Are Sustainable
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-07-01T10:34:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-01/guindos-says-spain-must-show-finances-services-are-sustainable.html
Spain  won’t resolve its funding
difficulties unless it shows its public finances and public
services are sustainable, Economy Minister Luis de Guindos said
during a conference in Navacerrada, near Madrid, today.  He also said last week’s summit of European leaders in
Brussels was “good” for the euro.  To contact the reporter on this story:
